{"tid":1564601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尻人華指示連登仔加開戰線","createTime":"2019-09-12T23:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T05:58:06.000Z","uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"229fa88d2e69ac779ab9d7e3084e47ef424775ad","tid":1564601,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:57:51.000Z","msg":"尻人華表示,單一國家根本不足夠,希望連登仔促使多一點國家一齊推人權法<br />\n<br />\n【邱騰華：單一國家改政策無礙港經貿地位】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2mcGYvc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2mcGYvc&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmEzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=06ffd901\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2mcGYvc</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國會將審議《#香港人權及民主法案》，提出根據香港實施「#一國兩制」的情況，審視美國給予香港的特殊待遇。商務及經濟發展局局長 #邱騰華 表示，香港經貿地位由《#基本法》賦予，包括獨立關稅區地位，個別國家的做法不會影響香港在憲制上的地位。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華指出，有留意美國國會討論香港情況，要求美國政府改變對香港的政策，但他不評論美方工作，認為香港做好「一國兩制」的工作，不需要其他政府給予意見。任何國家包括美國，在考慮對港政策時，均會先考慮自身利益。"},{"pid":"694602af60e959630dee91930087a39b14854a2b","tid":1564601,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:58:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"1a7570729c1bd8d18007eb9b30cf5c7ebc570544","tid":1564601,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T23:58:25.000Z","msg":"<span sty